Installing from a dpkg
==========================

On a Debian/Ubuntu system, install the .deb file from my repository.
Instructions are here:

http://www.tolaris.com/apt-repository/

Then run:

apt-get update
apt-get install apt-find-proxy

Installing manually
==========================

Add your proxies to apt-find-proxy.conf. Then install these files as:

sudo install apt-find-proxy /usr/bin/
sudo install -m 644 apt-find-proxy.conf /etc/apt/
sudo install -m 644 02proxy /etc/apt/apt.conf.d/
